	.responsively-lazy:not(img){position:relative;height:0}
	.responsively-lazy:not(img)>img{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%}
	img.responsively-lazy{width:100%;}

   #cmp_base {
		width: 500px;
		margin: 23px auto;
		padding: 20px;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		background: #F8F8F8;
	}
	#cmp_base .headline {
		font-size: 25px;
		line-height: 1.2;
		font-weight: 700;
	}
	#cmp_base .subheadline {
		font-size: 14px;
		line-height: 1.57;
	}
	#cmp_base img {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
	}
	#cmp_base .button {
		float: none;
		margin: 15px 50px;
		font-size: 14px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	#cmp_base .button a {
		margin: 0 auto;
		height: 46px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		line-height: 2.9;
	}
	#cmp_base .disclaimer {
		line-height: 1.5;
		font-size: 12px;
		color: #cccccc;
	}
	#cmp_base .disclaimer a {
		text-decoration: underline;
		color: #cccccc;
	}
	.socialmedia_cmp {
		margin-bottom: 5px;
		height: 110px;
		background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
		background-size: 100%;
		background-repeat: no-repeat;
		background-position: 50%;
	}
	.cmp-placeholder.inactive {
		display: none;
	}
	.cmp-default .socialmedia_cmp {
		height: 165px;
	}
	.cmp-default.twitter .socialmedia_cmp {
		height: 110px;
		background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
	}
	.cmp-default.youtube .socialmedia_cmp {
		height: 268px;
		background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
	}
	.cmp-default.facebook .socialmedia_cmp {
		height: 168px;
		background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
	}
	.cmp-default.instagram .socialmedia_cmp {
		height: 523px;
		background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
	}
  
        .bereichsteaser .content {
		padding: 0;
		border-bottom: 0;
	}
	.bereichsteaser .box {
		padding: 10px 0 10px 10px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #d9ddde;
	}
	.bereichsteaser .box img {float: left;}
	.bereichsteaser .box .headLine {
		display: block;
		overflow: hidden;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0 0 0 10px;
		height: 33px;
		line-height: 33px;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}
	* html .bereichsteaser .box .headLine {display: inline-block;}
